   225	| **Approval workflow framework** | Bill-payment approval workflow (D-6c), erosion approvals, expense approvals | **Order Management (§3.04)** — approval framework design lives there |
   226	| **Commission structure** | Labor markup decision (D-4) impacts commission calculations | **Commissions (§3.07)** — commission framework design lives there |
