    90	  3.0X.5  Recommendation summary
    91	  3.0X.6  Decisions for the leadership team
    92	  3.0X.7  Open questions / inputs needed
    93	```
    94	
    95	Plus a header table with: Decision density, Source coverage, KBM source path, Pivot source path.
