    98	
    99	Each in §3.0X.3 follows this exact structure:
   100	
   101	```
   102	### D-N. [Title — capability or design choice]
   103	
   104	**Source:** [KBM REQ-IDs from BRD with section reference]; [Pivot REQ-IDs from BRD with section reference]; [transcript references where applicable]
   105	
