   467	3\.03\.02 Current State Process
   468	
   469	Pivot currently processes ACH and wire payments in D365 with significant manual effort\. On check run days, the accounting team must create 42 individual journal entries manually to record ACH and wire transfers\. This process is time\-consuming, error\-prone, and creates bottlenecks in the payment processing workflow\.
   470	
   471	As documented during discovery: "They had started to cut and paste data into file to send to bank for ACH/Wires" – highlighting the manual effort required for the 42 individual journal entries on each check run day, representing a significant automation opportunity\.
   472	
