   474	
   475	- 42 manual journal entries required on check run day for ACH/wire processing
   476	- Manual cash application to AR invoices
   477	- Manual bank reconciliation processes
   478	- Credit card reconciliation requires manual effort each month
   479	- Tracy has created an integrated payables file format for Comerica but process is manual
   480	
