  1644	Pivot currently uses Adaptive Planning for budgeting and planning\. With the NetSuite Orion  implementation, they need to evaluate whether NetSuite Planning and Budgeting \(NSPB\) provides sufficient functionality to replace Adaptive Planning, or whether continuing with Adaptive Planning is the better approach\.
