  1657	
  1658	3\.13\.03 NetSuite Orion Solution
  1659	
  1660	NetSuite offers both native budgeting tools \(NSPB\) and proven integration with Adaptive Planning, providing flexibility in budgeting platform selection\.
  1661	
  1662	__NetSuite Planning and Budgeting \(NSPB\):__
  1663	NSPB is NetSuite's native planning and budgeting module with direct integration to GL actuals\. Capabilities include:
  1664	
  1665	- Multi\-year, multi\-scenario planning
  1666	- Driver\-based budgeting models
  1667	- Variance reporting \(budget vs\. actual\) Orion can generate backlog reports\.
  1668	- Department and project\-level budgets
  1669	- Rolling forecast capabilities
  1670	- Prior year data import from GL actuals
  1671	- Automated Budgeting & Forecasting: Pulls actuals directly from NetSuite, creates rolling forecasts, and identifies trends using embedded AI/ML for faster, more accurate plans\.
  1672	- __Scenario Modeling \("What\-If"\):__ Allows creation and comparison of multiple financial scenarios \(best, worst, baseline\) to prepare for uncertainty\.
  1673	- __Real\-Time Insights & Dashboards:__ Provides live dashboards and reporting with drill\-downs to visualize performance against targets\.
  1674	
  1675	__Adaptive Planning Integration:__
