  1111	
  1112	Pro forma invoices are a standard NetSuite feature designed for deposit collection. A pro forma invoice is issued to collect the deposit, which posts to a liability account (not revenue). When the final invoice is generated, the pro forma deposit is automatically applied, reducing the final amount due.
