123:**Pivot's approach.** Pivot articulated a comprehensive document management strategy: centralized storage associated with projects, customers, and vendors; version control with historical access; role-based access controls; document search by project, customer, type, keywords, or date ranges; and integration between document storage and transaction records. Pivot's emphasis reflects its operational scope, where project documentation, vendor agreements, and customer contracts are integral to daily workflow across multiple teams.
