_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Financial_Management.md:1125:Pivot currently uses global terms and conditions on quotes and invoices, but when Master Service Agreements \(MSAs\) dictate different terms, they must print quotes without the standard verbiage\. This manual workaround is inefficient and creates risk of using incorrect terms\.
